  <p>Block 9 makes the central policy distinction explicit. <strong>Mitigation</strong> = reduce the cause (cut emissions). <strong>Adaptation</strong> = reduce the impact (build resilience to changes already locked in). Chennai needs both, but the Brief audience (Greater Chennai Corporation) has real authority mostly over adaptation. Students draft the Recommendations section of the Brief — 3-5 specific, evidence-anchored, actionable GCC interventions for their chosen challenge.</p>
